"title": "8105: assurance, basis of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8105: assurance, basis of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The assurance of believers is based upon the certain knowledge of God revealed in creation and his mighty acts in history, upon the certainty of his promises, the vindication and resurrection of Christ and the inward testimony and outward demonstration of the power of the Holy Spirit.</p>\n<h2>Assurance is based upon the certain knowledge of God</h2>\n<h3>Assurance comes from knowing God through creation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:19-Rom1:20\">ROM 1:19–1:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:1-Ps19:4\">PSA 19:1–19:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:17\">ACT 14:17</a></p>\n<h3>Assurance comes from knowing God through his mighty acts</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod6:7\">EXO 6:7</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek37:13-Ezek37:14\">EZK 37:13–37:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod16:12\">EXO 16:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:46\">EXO 29:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh3:10-Josh3:13\">JOS 3:10–3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs20:13\">1KI 20:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:23\">ISA 49:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa60:16\">ISA 60:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:42\">EZK 20:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:26\">EZK 28:26</a></p>\n<h2>Assurance is based upon the certainty of God's word</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:8\">JHN 17:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:9-1John5:10\">1JN 5:9–5:10</a></p>\n<h3>Assurance because of God's oath</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:17\">HEB 6:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen50:24\">GEN 50:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:31\">DEU 4:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:7-Deut7:9\">DEU 7:7–7:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:30\">ACT 2:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:21\">HEB 7:21</a></p>\n<h3>Assurance because of God's promise</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh1:9\">JOS 1:9</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:20-Rom4:21\">ROM 4:20–4:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh23:10\">JOS 23:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh23:14\">JOS 23:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:25-2Sam7:26\">2SA 7:25–7:26</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr17:23-1Chr17:24\">1CH 17:23–17:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:56\">1KI 8:56</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:13\">PSA 145:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:6\">ISA 33:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:5\">HEB 13:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:12\">JAS 1:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:5\">JAS 2:5</a></p>\n<h2>Assurance is based upon God's vindication of his Son</h2>\n<h3>Assurance because of the resurrection of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:32\">ACT 2:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:31\">ACT 17:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:3\">ACT 1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:22\">ACT 1:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:39-Acts10:41\">ACT 10:39–10:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:30-Acts13:31\">ACT 13:30–13:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:4\">ROM 1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:3-1Cor15:7\">1CO 15:3–15:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:3\">1PE 1:3</a></p>\n<h3>Assurance because of the miracles of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:2-Matt11:6\">MAT 11:2–11:6</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:18-Luke7:23\">LUK 7:18–7:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:48\">JHN 4:48</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:38\">JHN 10:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:11\">JHN 14:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:30-John20:31\">JHN 20:30–20:31</a></p>\n<h2>Assurance comes through the work of the Holy Spirit</h2>\n<h3>The Holy Spirit assures believers by enabling outward demonstrations of God's power</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:4\">HEB 2:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:17-Mark16:18\">MRK 16:17–16:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:2-2Cor3:3\">2CO 3:2–3:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:5\">1TH 1:5</a></p>\n<h3>The Holy Spirit assures believers by giving inward conviction</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:16\">ROM 8:16</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:13\">1JN 4:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:26\">JHN 15:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:8-John16:11\">JHN 16:8–16:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:32\">ACT 5:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:6\">GAL 4:6</a></p>\n<h3>The Holy Spirit assures believers by sealing God's promise</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:13-Eph1:14\">EPH 1:13–1:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:8\">ACT 15:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:5\">ROM 5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:22\">2CO 1:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:5\">2CO 5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:30\">EPH 4:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:24\">1JN 3:24</a></p>\n<h2>Assurance based upon the testimony of God's people</h2>\n<h3>Assurance because of the testimony of eye-witnesses</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:16-2Pet1:19\">2PE 1:16–1:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod10:2\">EXO 10:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:2-Luke1:4\">LUK 1:2–1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:32-John1:34\">JHN 1:32–1:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:27\">JHN 15:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:35\">JHN 19:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:22\">ACT 1:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:20\">ACT 4:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:1\">1PE 5:1</a></p>\n<h3>Assurance because of the testimony of the apostles</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:14-Acts22:15\">ACT 22:14–22:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:6\">1CO 1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:1\">1CO 2:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:13\">1TH 2:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:5-1Tim2:7\">1TI 2:5–2:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:2\">REV 1:2</a></p>\n<h2>Assurance is based upon godly living</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:3-1John2:5\">1JN 2:3–2:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:23\">1JN 2:23</a> <em>right belief about Jesus Christ</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:29\">1JN 2:29</a> <em>righteousness</em><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:9\">1JN 3:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:18\">1JN 5:18</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:14-1John3:20\">1JN 3:14–3:20</a> <em>love for fellow believers</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:1\">1JN 5:1</a> <em>love for God the Father and God the Son</em></p>",
